    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. The exterior maintains a strong shine, though you may find a few minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free, with all electronic features and climate control systems functioning exactly as they should. Mechanically, the car is sound, providing a smooth ride and reliable performance for its next owner. It\u2019s a great option for someone seeking a dependable, attractive vehicle without the new-car price tag.",
