    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hi there! Are you looking for a dependable ride that\u2019s ready for its next big adventure? This car has been such a fantastic companion and is still in really solid shape. It\u2019s been well-cared for, drives beautifully, and is just waiting for someone new to take the wheel. It\u2019s perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways! I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home, so feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust E46 M3, powered by the iconic S54B32 3.2L inline-six. This unit features a high-compression head with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing, providing exceptional throttle response across the rev range. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers tactile shift throws, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to ensure structural rigidity under load. Maintenance is up to date with rod bearing clearance verified and a fresh valve adjustment. Equipped with a limited-slip differential and M-tuned suspension, this chassis delivers the precise feedback and neutral handling balance expected of the marque. A well-sorted driver's car with excellent mechanical bones.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Runs well.",
      "price": 34500.0,
