    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2016 BMW M2 in Long Beach Blue Metallic. This driver-focused machine has been kept in a climate-controlled garage and serviced exclusively at authorized centers, with a full folder of records included. The N55 engine pulls strongly through every gear, and the DCT transmission shifts with lightning precision. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a keen eye might spot a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with spirited weekend drives. Inside, the Dakota leather remains supple; there is only slight, natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All electronics, from the iDrive system to the heated seats, function perfectly. It sits on original 19-inch 437M wheels wrapped in Michelin Pilot Super Sports with plenty of tread remaining. This is a turn-key example ready for its next enthusiast owner who values a balance of performance and preservation.",
      "price": 38500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of exceptional mechanical integrity and aesthetic refinement. This automobile has been maintained to a rigorous standard, ensuring a driving experience that balances performance with enduring reliability. A distinguished choice for the discerning driver seeking sophisticated engineering and proven value.",
      "price": 34900.0,
