      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically robust example of the legendary S54-powered platform. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six pulls hard to its 8,000 RPM redline, featuring a recently serviced VANOS system and verified rod bearing tolerances. Power is managed via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis has been enhanced with rear subframe reinforcement and polyurethane bushings to mitigate common floor-pan fatigue. While the exterior shows honest signs of use consistent with a well-loved driver's car, the internal mechanicals and compression ratios remain excellent. It is a turn-key enthusiast machine ready for the canyons.",
